{"TopicId":197592,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Forum UI Changes","CreatedByName":"Clamp-o-Tron","CreatedById":201818,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T20:53:21Z","PageNum":12,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-27T13:59:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873218\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603755838\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278020\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AlamoVampire\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, AlamoVampire said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIm seeing them too. The one with a shield i think indicates moderator (at least i think so, i see that on like vanamonde for example) and the stop hand i think indicates a member who is new (i think) and requires moderator approval. This is my theory.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n184310262020\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, wow, I have a shield, too! That\u0027s really cool. But everyone knows where there is a shield, there\u0027s always some sort of primary weapon. Things that make you go hmmmm...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-27T15:28:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873444\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603807181\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, wow, I have a shield, too! That\u0027s really cool. But everyone knows where there is a shield, there\u0027s always some sort of primary weapon. Things that make you go hmmmm...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe banhammer? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-27T16:29:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873444\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603807181\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut everyone knows where there is a shield, there\u0027s always some sort of primary weapon.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm... that\u0027s no moon... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:targetretro:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/TargetRetro20px.png\u0022 title=\u0022:targetretro:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:blink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_blink.png\u0022 title=\u0022:blink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-28T15:06:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873228\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603756874\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/27/2020 at 12:01 AM, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/182413-bej-kerman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022182413\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/182413-bej-kerman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Bej Kerman\u003C/a\u003E, this is part of on-going work to get the latest version of the forum software running smoothly. Your question has been merged into the master thread.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd, you\u0027re not able to work on a backup, are you? \u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/X6NJkWbM1xk\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EWorking on the live thing sounds like a recipe for disaster.\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873226\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603756641\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/26/2020 at 11:57 PM, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873150\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197721\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603743675\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182413\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bej Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/26/2020 at 8:21 PM, Bej Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot sure where to post this (wouldn\u0027t be able to find the suitable topic anyway), but the forum is completely and totally broken. Is it so on your end? It\u0027s like there\u0027s no style, just text, massive bullet point lists and the default Chrome font.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nScreencap\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#2e3035;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/k4MOffr\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/k4MOffr\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nObligatory \u0022that looks better than correct\u0022 post.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(I don\u0027t actually think it looks \u003Cstrong\u003Ebetter\u003C/strong\u003E, but it does not look all that \u003Cstrong\u003Eworse\u003C/strong\u003E)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHonestly I agree\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-28T23:07:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t know from backups. I\u0027m not a techie. I just pass along what we\u0027re told.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T03:11:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nApparently there are technical reasons why the Gameplay sub cannot be set to default to chronological order. Our IT is still looking into alternatives but it\u0027s not looking promising.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DerkyJerkyWreaksHavoc","CreatedById":207646,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T15:45:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nActually i\u0027ve seen the forums UI Change quite a lot \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0and the day when the Forum was getting one of those U.I updates, the forum crashed on me and i couldn\u0027t get in but im fine now... Nice work! must be tough to be a moderator...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T18:13:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223874633\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603986315\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207646\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DAFATRONALDO2007 IN SPACE\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, DAFATRONALDO2007 IN SPACE said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... must be tough to be a moderator...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNaw.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DerkyJerkyWreaksHavoc","CreatedById":207646,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T18:15:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nreally. you probably get blasted with nothing but notifications and you gotta be everywhere at once. anyways, you do a pretty good job \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-02T21:33:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223870288\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603227201\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022201818\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Clamp-o-Tron\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/20/2020 at 3:53 PM, Clamp-o-Tron said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: To those who haven\u0027t seen, \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156657-hebarusan/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022156657\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156657-hebarusan/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HebaruSan\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0has an excellent Stylish configuration for a forums \u0022Dark Mode\u0022. Check it out, it\u0027s great!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022201818\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7649246180\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/197592-forum-ui-changes/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=3870460\u0026amp;embedComment=3870460\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022 style=\u0022height:294px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMinor announcement, since this thread has effectively become the home page for this dark theme:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWorking on this theme served as my personal introduction to CSS variables. I hadn\u0027t seen them in action before, but as I inspected the stock stylesheet in dev tools, it was plain that there was a powerful new syntax for styling, because IPS4\u0027s default theme is built entirely around CSS variables (to its great benefit). But I didn\u0027t yet know how they worked, and rather than risk making mistakes or delay\u00A0to re-learn CSS, I went about overriding the styles with familiar,\u00A0simple color literals instead, and made a note to come back and learn variables at some point.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nToday I finally went back and rewrote the whole thing to use IPS4\u0027s theme variables. The new code is\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Emuch\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0cleaner and shorter (just 100 lines), as well as more robust and consistent, because it now relies far more on the default theme to do the heavy lifting in places where I previously re-invented the wheel (such as the speech-bubble-tail shapes for popups). Pretty much the only downside is that I can\u0027t use \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003Ehsla()\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E in most places anymore because the stock theme uses \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003Ergb(var())\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E for most colors; \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003Ehsla()\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E is great for when you want to make a color brighter/darker or more/less saturated without changing the hue, or for mass-adjusting the hues of lots of related colors all at once (e.g., make a blue theme green).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe update is on the userstyles site, available via the \u0022Check for update\u0022 button in the Stylish settings. It should look pretty much identical, with a subtle difference here or there, plus styled scrollbars.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-02T22:28:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156657-hebarusan/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022156657\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156657-hebarusan/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HebaruSan\u003C/a\u003E So, to change colors at least, and maybe hide \u0026amp; resize elements, is it possible to just go in and substitute values?\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nIf so, would you mind if I poked it to see if I could manage a slightly different scheme with it? Might be easier to modify yours, than try to fix stuff broen in mine \u0026amp; nbz\u0027s... ~1200 lines of code \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd if so, would it be ok if I made it publicly available, with due credit and same license?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-02T22:48:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223876300\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221604356114\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277721\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156657-hebarusan/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022156657\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156657-hebarusan/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HebaruSan\u003C/a\u003E So, to change colors at least, and maybe hide \u0026amp; resize elements, is it possible to just go in and substitute values?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup, CSS variables make this pretty easy. These lines at the top set the variables, which are used and re-used across the default stylesheet to create consistent appearances for similar elements:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-css prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E    \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E--\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022kwd\u0022\u003Etheme-page_background\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022lit\u0022\u003E23\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E,\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022lit\u0022\u003E23\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E,\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022lit\u0022\u003E28\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n    \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E--\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022kwd\u0022\u003Etheme-text_light\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022lit\u0022\u003E148\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E,\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022lit\u0022\u003E148\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E,\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022lit\u0022\u003E184\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E;\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo see which\u00A0variable affects a particular element, press F12 (or Ctrl\u002BShift\u002BI) to bring up the dev tools, then Ctrl\u002BShift\u002BC and click the element, and the style info for it will appear in the Styles tab of the dev tools; look for lines containing \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003Ergb(var(--some-name))\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E, and the \u0022--some-name\u0022 part is the variable:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00221azNEFT.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002228.53\u0022 height=\u002291\u0022 width=\u0022319\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/1azNEFT.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSometimes you may need to navigate up or down in the DOM tree in the Elements tab to find the spot where a color is being set.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf so, would you mind if I poked it to see if I could manage a slightly different scheme with it? Might be easier to modify yours, than try to fix stuff broen in mine \u0026amp; nbz\u0027s... ~1200 lines of code \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFeel free!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EAnd if so, would it be ok if I made it publicly available, with due credit and same license?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe license is CC0, which as I understand it is public domain; go for it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-03T01:01:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanx \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156657-hebarusan/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022156657\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156657-hebarusan/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HebaruSan\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nOk...kewl... using the Inspector \u0026amp; Style Editor in FF, is basically how I hacked up nbz\u0027s theme, in the first place \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tux1","CreatedById":172521,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-15T19:57:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI haven\u0027t been on here in a few months, and when I get back, it looks completely different. In fact, it almost looks like :vomit: flat design. In unrelated news, I just got into orbit in an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E by myself.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: Wait no, I actually haven\u0027t been here in over a year. Time really flies by!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-11-15T19:58:27Z\u0022 title=\u002211/15/2020 07:58  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 15, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Tux1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eoops\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-15T20:17:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223881975\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198141\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605470252\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022172521\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tux1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 minutes ago, Tux1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI haven\u0027t been on here in a few months, and when I get back, it looks completely different. In fact, it almost looks like :vomit: flat design.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe software that the forum runs on had a UI update a while back. The general response was negative:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022201818\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6247333897\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/197592-forum-ui-changes/page/12/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:196px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-15T21:45:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223881997\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198141\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605471456\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealKerbal3x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, RealKerbal3x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe software that the forum runs on had a UI update a while back. The general response was negative:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022201818\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1727958260\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/197592-forum-ui-changes/page/12/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:195px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe response is ALWAYS negative, for every update\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-15T22:03:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOverlapping threads have been merged.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DeadJohn","CreatedById":201293,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-15T22:05:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223882036\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605476720\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 minutes ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe response is ALWAYS negative, for every update\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe you should adopt the forums \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Souptime","CreatedById":204451,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-16T16:18:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the new UI tbh\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-18T13:53:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223882036\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605476720\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/15/2020 at 4:45 PM, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe response is ALWAYS negative, for every update\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can please some of the people some of the time... and all of the people some of the time... but when the rooster crows in the morning...\u00A0 no wait..... something like that.\u00A0\u00A0 Doesn\u0027t matter what happens, somebody is always upset about something.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-18T14:43:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m officially used to it.\u00A0 The only thing that still bothers me is the change with how quotes are now put into pseudo-spoilers.\u00A0 All the other issues I\u0027ve had with the change have been fixed, like those horrendous, trendy round avatar images.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you asked me to point out what\u0027s different now, I probably couldn\u0027t.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-18T14:55:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223883195\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605710620\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m officially used to it.\u00A0 The only thing that still bothers me is the change with how quotes are now put into pseudo-spoilers.\u00A0 All the other issues I\u0027ve had with the change have been fixed, like those horrendous, trendy round avatar images.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you asked me to point out what\u0027s different now, I probably couldn\u0027t.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m still irritated by the movement of the edit button to a dropdown menu for no reason. But other than that, yeah, most of the problems I had when the update happened have been fixed now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-18T15:19:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s some behind-the-scenes stuff that I\u0027d still like to see adjusted to their former values, but I think IT has been very helpful and responsive to member feedback through this process.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"flart","CreatedById":181486,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-20T12:18:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStumbled upon\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forums.getpaint.net/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://forums.getpaint.net/\u003C/a\u003E, the\u00A0dark theme is soo nice!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022r7G2GtI.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002276.42\u0022 height=\u0022573\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/r7G2GtI.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022PHL0buA.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002241.17\u0022 height=\u0022308\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/PHL0buA.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-09-20T12:25:08Z\u0022 title=\u002209/20/2021 12:25  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 20, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by flart\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-20T12:41:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, cool! It looks just like our forum!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}